NE Groundfish fleet

groundfishNEFleet.Rmd
## Linking to GEOS 3.9.3, GDAL 3.5.2, PROJ 8.2.1; sf_use_s2() is TRUE

Species

The NE multispecies (Groundfish) FMP comprises the following species:

  • Atlantic Cod (COD)
  • Haddock (HAD)
  • Yellowtail Flounder (YTF)
  • Pollock (POL)
  • American Plaice (PLA)
  • Witch Flounder (WTF)
  • White Hake (WHK)
  • Winter Flounder (WIF)
  • Redfish (RED)
  • Atlantic Halibut (HAL)

Non target species

  • Windowpane flounder (WPF)
  • Ocean Pout (OPT)
  • Atlantic Wolffish (WOL)

These GEARCAT(s) associated with groundfish species are:

  • Bottom Trawl
  • Sink Gillnet

** Still need to separate some species (skates, sharks) **
